{
  "texts": [
    "In this process, the feature extractor is trained on a large dataset of fundus images without the need for manual annotations.",
    "MoCo v2 uses a momentum-based contrastive learning framework, where the pretrain framework in the fundus model learns to create positive and negative pairs of image patches from the same image 59.",
    "We laid out the experimental setup in our pretrain process.",
    "We predominantly followed the experimental settings of MoCo v2, but adopted different approaches in data augmentation and certain hyperparameter selections.",
    "We used the k-nearest neighbors monitor as a tool for self-supervised evaluation once per epoch."
  ]
}